# PokeTeamDex — domain reference (Dart)

## PokéAPI patterns

```dart
const base = 'https://pokeapi.co/api/v2';
// Full list (cache on first launch, TTL 24h):
GET $base/pokemon?limit=10000&offset=0
// Detail (cache on access, TTL 7d for static, 24h for list):
GET $base/pokemon/{id}           // → sprites, stats, moves, abilities
GET $base/pokemon-species/{id}   // → dex entries, evolution_chain url, gender_rate
GET $base/evolution-chain/{id}
GET $base/{move|ability|item|type|nature|location}/{id}

// Sprites
sprites.other['official-artwork'].front_default   // official art
sprites.other['official-artwork'].front_shiny
sprites.front_default  // small sprite
sprites.front_shiny
```

## Stat formula

```dart
// HP
floor(((2*base + iv + floor(ev/4)) * level / 100)) + level + 10
// Other stats
floor((floor(((2*base + iv + floor(ev/4)) * level / 100)) + 5) * natureMod)
// natureMod: 1.1=boosted  0.9=reduced  1.0=neutral
```

