## Showdown export format

```text
{Nickname} ({Species}) @ {Held Item}   ← if nickname==species: no parens
Ability: {Ability}
Level: {Level}
Shiny: Yes                             ← omit if not shiny
Nature: {Nature}
EVs: 252 SpA / 252 Spe                 ← omit 0-EV stats
- Move1
- Move2
- Move3
- Move4
```

## Gender rate mapping (`pokemon-species.gender_rate`)

```text
-1 → Genderless | 0 → Male only | 8 → Female only | 1-7 → Male/Female
```

## Navigation routes

```text
/pokedex → /pokedex/:id
/moves → /moves/:id
/items → /items/:id
/abilities/:id   (modal/sheet)
/reference       (tabs: types | natures | locations)
/teams → /teams/:teamId → /teams/:teamId/slots/:slotIndex
```

